00:17:44,625 --> 00:17:45,958
You have a
relationship?

251
00:17:46,041 --> 00:17:50,416
Not at all! It's just
that... you seemed...

252
00:17:50,500 --> 00:17:53,833
Let's just say he did me
a great favor once...

253
00:17:53,916 --> 00:17:56,625
I was alone in Alta, on a
mission for the Empress,

254
00:17:56,708 --> 00:17:59,083
and it was he who
came to my aid...

255
00:17:59,166 --> 00:18:02,541
I honestly believe I wouldn't
be the woman I am today

256
00:18:02,625 --> 00:18:04,125
were it
not for him.

257
00:18:04,208 --> 00:18:06,750
Is that the reason
you welcomed us?

258
00:18:06,833 --> 00:18:09,916
Yes... but there was
another reason as well...

259
00:18:10,000 --> 00:18:12,208
today the Empress told
me Vatican emissaries

260
00:18:12,291 --> 00:18:15,416
would be arriving... and
would need protection.

261
00:18:15,500 --> 00:18:16,958
The Empress
said that?

262
00:18:18,125 --> 00:18:19,458
That's odd...

263
00:18:19,541 --> 00:18:21,541
it's almost as if the Empress
knew something like this

264
00:18:21,625 --> 00:18:23,416
was going to happen,
and took the precaution

265
00:18:23,500 --> 00:18:25,333
of providing
us sanctuary.

266
00:18:25,416 --> 00:18:28,750
I don't understand it
all myself... but...

267
00:18:28,833 --> 00:18:30,083
Her Majesty is
said to be aware

268
00:18:30,166 --> 00:18:32,875
of everything that
happens in her Empire.

269
00:18:32,958 --> 00:18:35,708
Perhaps she foresaw your
predicament... who can say?

270
00:18:35,791 --> 00:18:37,458
It makes no
difference...

271
00:18:37,541 --> 00:18:40,458
to a Methuselah she is the
sole empress of eternity

272
00:18:40,541 --> 00:18:43,625
and our royal mother...
From past to present...

273
00:18:43,708 --> 00:18:46,958
from present unto eternity...
she rules the Empire...

274
00:18:47,041 --> 00:18:48,625
and her
word is law.

275
00:18:48,708 --> 00:18:52,791
At her command I will
protect you with my life.

276
00:18:55,666 --> 00:18:58,166
That is my duty
and my privilege...

277
00:18:58,250 --> 00:19:01,750
as a member of an
Imperial noble house...

278
00:19:01,833 --> 00:19:03,708
Come... you should
finish your bath

279
00:19:03,791 --> 00:19:05,750
before you become
light-headed...

280
00:19:05,833 --> 00:19:10,833
Oh! Alright!

281
00:19:12,291 --> 00:19:14,625
Excuse me, but is
that a battle scar...?

282
00:19:14,708 --> 00:19:17,791
Forgive me for prying, but
it's amazing that a Terran

283
00:19:17,875 --> 00:19:19,833
could survive
such a wound!

284
00:19:20,791 --> 00:19:24,625
Oh, that, I've had that all
my life... It's a birthmark.

285
00:19:24,708 --> 00:19:26,875
Birthmark?

286
00:19:29,583 --> 00:19:32,333
It's a very
pretty star shape.

287
00:19:39,916 --> 00:19:42,916
Then you still haven't
located the Earl of Memphis

288
00:19:43,000 --> 00:19:44,750
or the envoys
from the Vatican?

289
00:19:44,833 --> 00:19:46,333
No, Majesty, but
we are sweeping

290
00:19:46,416 --> 00:19:48,583
the urban areas
thoroughly.

291
00:19:48,666 --> 00:19:51,958
I can assure you that it's
only a matter of time.

292
00:19:52,041 --> 00:19:55,666
No matter... Everything
is going as planned...

293
00:19:55,750 --> 00:19:59,416
You look tired...
Go now and rest.

294
00:20:07,250 --> 00:20:10,625
I know you're back
there. Who are you?

295
00:20:10,708 --> 00:20:12,750
It didn't seem likely we'd
be granted an audience

296
00:20:12,833 --> 00:20:15,583
through normal channels, so
I decided to bypass them...

297
00:20:15,666 --> 00:20:16,833
I beg your
pardon...

298
00:20:16,916 --> 00:20:19,583
please forgive me for
intruding unannounced.

299
00:20:19,666 --> 00:20:22,416
A Terran...? What
do you want?

300
00:20:22,500 --> 00:20:24,541
I am called
Father Abel...

301
00:20:24,625 --> 00:20:28,375
I was sent by the Vatican
Ministry of Holy Affairs.

302
00:20:28,458 --> 00:20:31,625
I see. So my message
arrived safely...

303
00:20:31,708 --> 00:20:34,750
But before we get
to other matters...

304
00:20:34,833 --> 00:20:37,625
I think it would be best if
you would explain the incident

305
00:20:37,708 --> 00:20:40,083
at the Duchess of
Moldova's mansion...

306
00:20:40,166 --> 00:20:43,333
I'm sure your version would
be most enlightening...

307
00:20:43,416 --> 00:20:44,833
man of the Vatican.

308
00:20:44,916 --> 00:20:48,416
Before I do... perhaps you
would enlighten me on a point.

309
00:20:48,500 --> 00:20:49,583
Hm?

310
00:20:49,666 --> 00:20:51,958
Just who are you, m'lady?

311
00:20:52,041 --> 00:20:55,375
What's that...? What are
you talking about...?

312
00:20:55,458 --> 00:20:58,458
I am the one ruler of the
Empire of the True Race...

313
00:20:58,541 --> 00:21:01,666
Augusta Vradica,
the first and only...

314
00:21:01,750 --> 00:21:03,291
Is that so...?

315
00:21:03,375 --> 00:21:06,666
Am I really to believe
that you're the Empress?

316
00:21:06,750 --> 00:21:12,208
Is this a jest...?
No... you're serious...

317
00:21:12,291 --> 00:21:14,333
What do you know, priest?

318
00:21:14,416 --> 00:21:16,083
Your Majesty!

319
00:21:16,166 --> 00:21:18,125
Forgive me, but an
intruder has been reported

320
00:21:18,208 --> 00:21:20,166
in the inner
courtyard...

321
00:21:23,416 --> 00:21:25,666
Who are you?!

322
00:21:28,333 --> 00:21:29,791
You won't escape me!

323
00:21:29,875 --> 00:21:31,166
Enough, Baibals!

324
00:21:33,041 --> 00:21:35,833
I don't want him
harmed in any way!

325
00:21:56,625 --> 00:22:00,166
Is it possible...?
Is he...?

326
00:23:52,666 --> 00:23:57,916
Next- Episode 16:
The Night Lords: Part Two.

327
00:23:58,000 --> 00:23:59,500
Twilight of the Capital.

328
00:23:59,583 --> 00:24:01,750
Avert not thine eyes.

